383
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:31,060
<font color="#ffff00">Aku kembali ke kamar./ Hati-hati kakimu.</font>

384
00:41:31,160 --> 00:41:32,520
<font color="#ffff00">Kakinya sungguh tak masalah?</font>

385
00:41:47,440 --> 00:41:50,480
<font color="#ffff00">A Si, suasana hatimu sedang bagus.</font>

386
