389
00:42:08,520 --> 00:42:09,822
<font color="#ffff00">Begitu itu bagaimana?</font>

390
00:42:11,673 --> 00:42:13,093
<font color="#ffff00">Ya begitu.</font>

391
00:42:14,360 --> 00:42:17,360
